name: Artheria
note:
updated
Lead: Thomas Iuliano
Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/in/thomas-iuliano-b6659984/
Email: iulianothomas@gmail.com
Comments: The last communication date 12.12.2023
Message: Hello Alona,

I would like to express my appreciation for your recent offer. However, at this point in time, we currently do not require that kind of services. Nonetheless, we would like to keep your proposal and contact details for future reference.

Similarly, I would like to take this opportunity to introduce our own outsourcing services in both 3D and 2D. Our services are designed to assist you in developing your projects faster and more efficiently.

Our range of services includes 3D sculpture, low poly modeling, texturing, shading, rigging, and optimization. Additionally, we can provide concept art, illustration and icon design, mood boards, storyboards, character/environment/prop design, and UI design. Throughout the project, you will have the opportunity to follow the work-in-progress and provide real-time feedback, ensuring smooth collaboration and meeting deadlines effectively.

To get a better understanding of our approach to asset creation, you can view our recent work on our outsourcing asset 3D https://www.artheria.it/outsourcing-asset-3d/ and outsourcing asset 2D https://www.artheria.it/outsourcing-asset-2d/.

If you believe that our services can assist you in realizing your projects, I would be more than happy to arrange a meeting call.
Thank you for your time, and have a pleasant day.
Best regards, Thomas
Company Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/company/artheria/
Site Company: https://www.artheria.it/
